reviewText: A fun film inspired by the classic Sci-Fi films of the 50's with a Bill Black style. Campy...YES! Great Make-up...YES! Fun story...YES! Watch this if you like to discover fun film gems!

If you like the old, sometimes curiously weird, jungle movies shot on studiobound sets by low-end film companies during the 1940's and 50's, you can't pass this one by. It's a very entertaining retro movie love letter. I wish it had been longer!

Big old Gorilla Movie! Here is looking back to the good old days when movies were fun. This is a old school great gorilla movie featuring TWO gorillas in a life and death struggle over a beauty. What more could a fan ask for?
